item.title: Getting on someone elses server!
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Adam Adam
item.description:
@Mod_Adam wrote:

Get Hamachi, put in there server info on Hamachi, the Open MoparScape, click File — New Server — Enter their Server Ip — Make a S/N and Password — Login — Enjoy.
